    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const job = $input.item.json;\nconst MY_RESUME = `\nNAME: Md. Aman Uddin Siyam\nEDUCATION:\nBSc in Computer Science & Engineering — IUBAT, Dhaka, Bangladesh (2022 - Present)\nCGPA: 3.24\nSKILLS:\nAI & ML: Python, PyTorch, TensorFlow, scikit-learn, NumPy, Pandas, OpenCV, LangChain, LlamaIndex\nLLMs & RAG: Llama 3, Groq, Qdrant (Vector DB), RAG Architectures, SHAP (XAI)\nMLOps: Docker, FastAPI, Flask, GitHub Actions (CI/CD), Weights & Biases\nFull Stack: React, Next.js 14, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, TypeScript\nResearch: Signal Processing, EDA, Feature Engineering, Few-Shot Learning, Edge AI\nPROJECTS:\n1. BAT-Track — Lightweight UAV object tracking, 39.3 FPS, 60.5% power reduction, 64.2% IoU accuracy.\n2. Financial RAG Analyst — Production RAG pipeline, LlamaIndex + Qdrant + Llama 3, SEC 10-K analysis, Dockerized.\n3. DebateArena — Real-time AI-judged debate platform, Socket.IO, Gemini API, Next.js 14 + Express.js.\n4. Edge-ViT-FSL — Few-shot plant disease diagnosis, under 10MB, 22.13 FPS, 73.93% cross-domain accuracy.\n5. PCOS Detection — XGBoost+LightGBM+CatBoost ensemble, AUROC 0.976.\nPUBLICATIONS:\n- Voice-Based Parkinson's Disease Detection (SVM & XGBoost)\n- Clinical vs. Ultrasound for PCOS Detection (Accepted ICCIT)\n- Cosmetic Chemical Carcinogenicity ML Pipeline (Accepted ICCIT)\n- LENS-Guard: Lightweight VAE-CNN for Threat Detection (Accepted ICECTE)\n`;\n\nconst title = job.title || '';\nconst company = job.company || '';\nconst location = job.location || '';\nconst description = (job.description || '').substring(0, 500);\nconst matchReasons = Array.isArray(job.match_reasons)\n  ? job.match_reasons.join(', ')\n  : (job.match_reasons || '');\n\nconst prompt = `You are an expert cover letter writer for ML/AI roles.\nWrite a concise, non-generic cover letter (200-250 words maximum) for this job.\nCANDIDATE RESUME:\n${MY_RESUME}\nJOB:\nTitle: ${title}\nCompany: ${company}\nLocation: ${location}\nMatch reasons: ${matchReasons}\nDescription excerpt: ${description}\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Never open with \"I am writing to express my interest\"\n- Lead with a specific technical accomplishment from the resume that directly matches the role\n- Mention the company name naturally once\n- Reference 1-2 specific projects by name if relevant\n- End with one concrete question about their ML infrastructure or team\n- No fluff, no filler sentences\n- Plain text only, no markdown, no bullet points\nWrite the cover letter now:`;\n\nconst requestBody = {\n  model: \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n  temperature: 0.4,\n  max_tokens: 600,\n  messages: [\n    {\n      role: \"user\",\n      content: prompt\n    }\n  ]\n};\n\nreturn [{ json: {\n  requestBody,\n  stored_job_id: job.job_id,\n  stored_title: job.title,\n  stored_company: job.company,\n  stored_url: job.url,\n  stored_source: job.source,\n  stored_score: job.score,\n  stored_recommendation: job.recommendation,\n  stored_match_reasons: job.match_reasons,\n  stored_missing_skills: job.missing_skills,\n  stored_one_line_summary: job.one_line_summary\n} }];"
